navigationContext.accessibilityText: Open article: Freelance Forward 2023 | Upwork by upwork.com

text.text:
Coming down the stretch of another year, the freelance economy continues to surge, showcasing robust growth and an increasingly influential presence in shaping the #FutureOfWork. Upwork shared our 2023 Freelance Forward report encapsulating the phenomenal strides and pivotal moments and trends defining the U.S. freelance workforce today.
 
Here's a glimpse:
 
 � � A record-breaking 64 million Americans embraced freelancing, making up 38% of the U.S. workforce and contributing an astounding $1.27 trillion to the economy!
 
 � � 20% of freelancers are consistently leveraging #generativeAI tools, showcasing a commitment to cutting-edge technology and upskilling themselves in this era of #GenAI.
 
 � � The freelance community continues to diversify and evolve, with 52% of Gen Z professionals and 44% of Millennials engaging in freelance work in 2023. Remarkably, 17% of all freelancers are aged 59 or older, highlighting the inclusive nature of freelancing.
 
 � � Enthusiasm for #freelancing as a career continues to soar, with over 85% of freelancers saying the best days are ahead for freelancing, reflecting the growing recognition and positivity surrounding freelance work.
 
Against this exciting backdrop of a growing broader freelance economy, I’m so proud of the work Upwork has done in 2023 to build a better way to not only freelance but work in any way that meets professionals’ and businesses’ evolving needs:
 
 � � 1 Million+ Projects Completed: Our awesome community of independent talent and businesses worked together across 125+ categories, 10,000+ skills and 180+ countries. 
 
 � � AI Advancements: We collaborated with OpenAI to launch OpenAI Experts on Upwork; extended our AI Services hub as a one-stop shop for AI work; launched our first slate of #GenAI-powered tools, including a job post generator and Upwork Chat Pro; and partnered with companies like Miro, ClickUp, Jasper, Amazon, Adobe, Udemy and Coursera to deliver talent outfitted with the best #generativeAI tools and resources who can tackle organizations’ boldest AI initiatives. This is just the beginning of our journey to make Upwork the premier destination for AI talent and work opportunities.
 
 � � Enterprise Solutions: Upwork's Enterprise Suite evolved, including strategic partnerships with SAP Fieldglass and Flextrack Inc, integrations, and a new user-centric dashboard.
 
For more details, explore key findings in our Freelance Forward 2023 report: https://lnkd.in/g_VpzDzw. 
Or see our blog post chronicling Upwork’s year in review: https://lnkd.in/gEt_r3hY.
 
This year has been marked by tremendous growth and innovation in the freelance and broader work landscape. Thank you to our incredible Upwork team and to all of our amazing, innovative customers who remain on the cutting-edge of the #FutureOfWork!
